join aurora (neutral) right [animation="Bounce In"]
aurora: System integrity at 84%... The rift waves are collapsing our localized sector.
aurora: Wait! A localized foreign signature... Your physical structure is... entirely made of shifting shadows?
aurora (surprised): This is fascinating. Your shadow-energy is actively stabilizing my matrix core. The interference is fading!
join kira (neutral) left [animation="Slide Left In"]
kira: Hey! Don't keep all the fun to yourself! 
kira: My sunfire sensors picked up a massive stability spike. Is this the shadowy foreign traveler everyone's whisperin' about?
aurora (blush): Kira, please maintain physical boundary protocols. The traveler's dark presence is highly reactive.
kira (blush): Aw, look at him glitching out! The way his shadow-cloak flutters is so cool. Let me get closer and feel it!
- Step closer to Aurora to stabilize her matrix.
	aurora (blush): Ah... the system warming... it's not just data. My core temperature is rising.
	aurora (happy): Thank you, Ren. The localized instability has subsided to negligible levels.
	kira: Hey, no fair! I want some shadow-warmth too!
- Step towards Kira and playfully tease her.
	kira (blush): Whoa, easy! Those soft glowing eyes of yours are way too intense from this close. My ears are twitching!
	aurora (sad): Traveler, please do not neglect my core calibration... the alignment is still delicate.
[background path="res://bgs/rift.jpg" fade="1.5"]
aurora (neutral): Look! The rift is shifting us toward the sacred outer sanctums.
