elara: May the starlight guide us. The Nexus has chosen a sanctum of pure silence.
selene: Quiet indeed, Elara. But with our shadowy guest, this sanctuary might become rather... exquisite.
elara (blush): Selene! Please, show some restraint. The sheer silk of my healing vestments is already reacting to this dense atmosphere.
selene (blush): Oh? And what of your glowing energy, healer? It's radiating straight toward the traveler.
